+### 13.2 Swarm composition form
+
+Inputs:
+
+```ts
+type SwarmLaunchSpec = {
+  projectId: string;
+  planId?: string;
+  beadScope?: {
+    priorities?: number[];
+    labels?: string[];
+    beadIds?: string[];
+    excludeBeadIds?: string[];
